actual_SQL: SELECT aircraft_type_match.aircraft_type FROM aircraft_type_match INNER JOIN dc_aircraft_model ON aircraft_type_match.`code` = dc_aircraft_model.aircraft_type WHERE name = "Hawker 400XP" LIMIT 1;
